data.description: Look no further! This adorable 3 bedroom home features lots of natural light, hardwood flooring throughout most of the main floor, a cozy family room in the lower level, and an open outdoor area with a three-season porch, perfect for entertaining. Non-conforming 4th bedroom and abundant storage in the lower level. Enjoy the convenience of Abdella Park just across the street, complete with basketball, baseball, and tennis courts. Schedule your private tour today!
